ou so that you had to shout 'cos the - the sound waves be going past him - it wouldn't be hitting his ears - it'd be going past his ears. And I can still to this day, with a few little errors, I can repeat the first ten to fourteen pages of the manual dri
ll book and give it you word for word. I can remember it }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12937361\charrsid7472631 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4400345\charrsid7472631 
o well and - I can read a book -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8484072 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4400345\charrsid7472631 Would you have liked a better education?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1133603 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4400345\charrsid7472631 
I would have liked to have gone to a public school. I'd have liked to have gone to a public school because - I was - in those days - I was very interested in athletes - in athletics I should say. I was - I could swim - I swam -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8484072 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4400345\charrsid7472631 You took part in sport did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1133603 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4400345\charrsid7472631 
I - I swam for the school. I got certificates for swimming, I got certificates for running. And I 
think that - 'course as I said hindsight, but I think if'd have had the chance to go to boarding school and mix with boys - of a - higher intellect - I think I'd got a - done me a world of good. With a chance of -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8484072 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4400345\charrsid7472631 This was near your home was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1133603 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4400345\charrsid7472631 
It was quite close, yes. With a chance to go on to a university. Because I find out - I've found out - whether its an advantage I don't know - but I can read the dryest - books that's as dry as dust - a person pick - another person'd pick it up and read t
he title and throw it away on the floor - I can read it. I remember a case in point where a little knowledge is dangerous. I was in - Egypt and I come down from the desert.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8484072 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4400345\charrsid7472631 How did you get to school - was it far away?
