ight it was - a little star was put in it for the each week you went and if you didn't have enough }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2379883\charrsid7472631 attendances}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
