ham sandwich and then you all sat down - each one got a bag, and so you all got the same, and you sat down round the talle and then they serve you with tea or whatever it was. And then after it was all over - you sang songs and all sorts of thing happened
 
and then as you came out there was teachers there with big tea chests and as each child came out through the door they'd be given a present. A little girl's get a doll. A boy'd get a wooden fire engine or a wooden en - train. Everybody got something. Only
 small things but -
