 person who became what they called head cook and bottle washer and took all the reins of office and - oh, were in their element doing it, but I used to - I used to think to myself remember a friend of mine, a boy, I've never forgot him - I remember a fri
end - a friend of mine - a very dear friend of mine - he was a same - sim -
